19:
Ahahaha, what was that? You're
pretty weird.
24: Kitty, you think so too, right?
30:
Why don't you give that kitten a
name?
34: Isn't Kitty fine? I think it's cute.
39:
Sure, it is, but... You know, you're
pretty weird yourself.
43:
Okay, that's enough about that. I
want to hear more about the
dragon that flies through the sky.
47:
That story again? I don't mind, but
you should play the game yourself. I
can lend you my phone. It's old, but
it works.
51:
...That's nice of you, but I'd rather
hear you tell it. After all...
60:
Sorry... It looks like I wasn't careful
enough.
66:
Don't touch him. I didn't tell him
anything, so there's no reason to.
69:
If it was a friend you wished for, we
could have found one for you. I
believe one of the believers has a
daughter around your age.
72: ...I don't need you to do that.
80:
Thanks for playing with me. I had a
really fun time.
89:
Even a fourteen-year-old kid like me
knew something about the whole
situation was off.
90:
I should've been able to find out
what had happened to him... I
could've talked to an adult or even
followed after him.
91:
Instead, I was too afraid to find out if
I had done something wrong. So I
began to avoid the park.
94:
Nao wouldn't stop crying about the
small kitten that passed away.
95:
Our mom comforted me, patting me
on the back. "If only we'd noticed it
sooner," she said.
96:
...I know better than anyone that I'm
not a kind person at all.
99: But it's not too late to try.
103:
I want to be a better person, like
everyone else around me!
124: I won't let you do as you please...
127:
The world Oghir and I wanted... will
be ours...
130:
So that nothing will be taken from us
ever again.
145:
The whole place is falling apart!
We're falling outta the sky!
168:
Are you kidding me? I thought we
fixed the problem!
175:
Nova, please lend me your
assistance.
193:
All right, the gate's stable! You
should be able to cross just fine!
197:
Tohru! Where are the people you
rescued from the river?
201:
My mom and dad are with them! So
are Sho's and Ayumu's families!
204:
You have family you care about too,
don't you? Then help us!
209:
Are you seriously suggesting we
bring everyone with us?
214:
As many as we can, including all the
people who escaped from the
shelter!
219:
Gravity user. Your power will come in
handy. Follow me.
224:
What, you think you can just boss
me around? I was gonna help
anyway!
229:
I'll grab all the people inside the
building!
233:
We gotta find Mr. Takamori too!
Come on!
243:
Nova... How many people can we
bring with us?
247:
...The gate should hold. Your odds of
saving everyone aren't great, but I'll
do everything I can to help.
258: Yeah, I'm with you on this.
266:
I'm probably about to do the wrong
thing.
275: Do you what you have to, Stella.
280: Stella? What are you up to—
284: By the will of the Stars, I order you...
